    <section class="bg-light py-2 border-bottom">
      <div class="container px-5 my-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
          <p align="justify">
            Welcome to MessMate, your one-stop platform for actively
            participating in shaping the mess menu at VIT Vellore! We believe
            that a well-balanced, nutritious, and diverse menu enhances the
            student experience. This system allows you to suggest, review, and
            contribute to the finalization of the weekly mess menu. Your inputs
            play a crucial role in ensuring that the food served aligns with the
            preferences and dietary needs of the students. Let’s work together
            to create a menu that is both delicious and wholesome!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-light py-2 border-bottom">
      <div class="container px-5 my-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
