                      carbohydrates, vegetables, and essential nutrients
                    </h6>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="card" style="height: 8rem; width: 18rem">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Diversity in Cuisine</h5>
