                      preferences
                    </h6>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="card" style="height: 8rem; width: 18rem">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Health Considerations</h5>
                    <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
                      Avoid excessive oily, fried, or overly spicy food to
                      maintain a healthy diet
                    </h6>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td>
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Feasibility & Availability</h5>
                    <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
                      Consider ingredients that are seasonally available and
                      practical for large-scale preparation
                    </h6>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Meal-Time Suitability</h5>
                    <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
                      Suggest dishes appropriate for breakfast, lunch, snacks,
                      and dinner
                    </h6>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Dietary Preferences</h5>
                    <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">
                      Keep in mind vegetarian, vegan, and other dietary
                      requirements for inclusivity
                    </h6>
                  </div>
